2026-05-01T20:55:51.8346170Z 22    <!--
2026-05-01T20:55:51.8366002Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-01T20:55:51.8366803Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-01T20:55:51.8367483Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-01T20:55:51.8368271Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-01T20:55:51.8369367Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-01T20:55:51.8370150Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-01T20:55:51.8370949Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-01T20:55:51.8371732Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-01T20:55:51.8372502Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-01T20:55:51.8373234Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-01T20:55:51.8373800Z 33    -->
2026-05-01T20:55:51.8374394Z 34    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
